PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food of DEBORAH SHERREN (JONES) WHALE of Alma, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Farm Credit Canada to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Eleanor M.
